"{\"uid\": \"balls.ie-olympics-ciara-mcging-illness-606906\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"What makes the Olympics so special is that it only comes every 4 years.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 71, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 11, \"to\": 23}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anticipation builds up and the World gathers to watch the best athletes compete for medals.\", \"from\": 72, \"to\": 163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Anticipation\", \"from\": 72, \"to\": 84}, {\"ngram\": \"the World\", \"from\": 99, \"to\": 108}, {\"ngram\": \"the best athletes\", \"from\": 126, \"to\": 143}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The four-year cycle is also what makes the Olympics so cruel.\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 226, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The four-year cycle\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 184}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 204, \"to\": 216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can be prepared for the whole time leading up to the Olympics, be ready to compete but one minor issue or illness can ruin four years of hard-work and dedication.\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the whole time\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 265}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 292}, {\"ngram\": \"one minor issue\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 333}, {\"ngram\": \"illness\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"four years\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"hard-work\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 377}, {\"ngram\": \"dedication\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's something Irish diver Ciara McGing found out the hard way unfortunately ahead of her 10m platform diving preliminary round.\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ciara\", \"score\": 0.9999998966357051, \"rank\": 1.0333389923212245e-07, \"text\": \"Ciara\", \"ty