 been very ill the last 48 hours, hooked up to a drip and everything so I am very grateful for the doctors at Team Ireland that I even got here today because this time yesterday I would not have been here so I am just proud.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1532, \"end\": 1544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.723035391883841e-14, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a drip\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1490}, {\"ngram\": \"the doctors\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone at the village behind me got me here this morning.\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just the timing like I do not want to use it as an excuse but like it's obviously not an ideal situation.\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1818, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just the timing\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"an excuse\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1770}, {\"ngram\": \"an ideal situation\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite everything seemingly going against Ciara McGing she was always determined to compete even if it wasn't to her best capabilities.\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1956, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1863, \"end\": 1868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ciara\", \"score\": 0.9999998966357051, \"rank\": 1.0333389923212245e-07, \"text\": \"Ciara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ciara\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ciara\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"her best capabilities\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1955}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd never withdraw.\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1977, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You would have had to fight me not to get on that 10 metre, so no I am just very grateful it was yesterday and not this morning.\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that 10 metre\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ciara McGing said she never considered not diving today despite being \\\"very ill\\\" and needing a drip over the last 48 hours.\\ud83d\\udcf1 Reporthttps://t.co/IJZ4Z7xbOP#Paris2024#olympics#olympicgamespic.twitter.com/rrDuuz7urL - RT\\u00c9 Sport (@RTEsport)August 5, 2024 It's fair to say that McGing's preparation could not have gone much worse and everyone knows she can perform better than she was capable of this time around.\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2108, \"end\": 2113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ciara\", \"score\": 0.9999998966357051, \"rank\": 1.0333389923212245e-07, \"text\": \"Ciara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ciara\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ciara\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a drip\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"the last 48 hours\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"@RTEsport)August\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2350}, {\"ngram\": \"McGing's preparation\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2401}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2445}, {\"ngram\": \"this time\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully she will get the opportunity in four years to prove that.\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2559}, {\"ngram\": \"four years\", \"from